<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Display Student Page</title>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
</head>
<body>

<form action="" method="post">
<p>Setup the service details. In Kubernetes, each service
is given a unique IP address known as the Cluster IP and
a service port number (aka &quot;port&quot;) that was specified during the service declaration.
Alternatively, you may enter a Node IP address of the DNS name of the service.
What you enter here depends on the type of Kubernetes service that you are testing.
</p>
<p>ClusterIP: internal service, using cluster IP or service name
FQDN=&lt;service-name&gt;.&lt;namespace-name&gt;.svc.cluster.local or shorthand this by just using the service name</p>
<p>Node IP: internal/external service, using IP of a node within the cluster</p>
<p>Load Balancer: external service, use external IP address of service or </p>
<br/><label for="ip-textbox">ClusterIP, NodeIP or DNS:</label>
<input id="ip-textbox" name="ip-textbox" type="text" value="0.0.0.0" />
<br/><label for="service-port-textbox">Service Port:</label>
<input id="service-port-textbox" name="service-port-textbox" type="text" value="1339" />
<br/><label for="service-path-textbox">Path (if reqd):</label>
<span id="path-prefix"></span><input id="service-path-textbox" name="service-path-textbox" type="text" value="" />
<br/>JSON Body:<input id="post-body-textbox" name="post-body-textbox" type="text" /><input id="post-button" type="button" value="POST"/>
<br/><input id="get-button" type="button" value="GET"/>
<br/>JSON Body:<input id="put-body-textbox" name="put-body-textbox" type="text" /><input id="put-button" type="button" value="PUT"/>
<br/><input id="delete-button" type="button" value="DELETE"/>
</form>
<div id="status" border=1>Status Waiting...</div>

<br/>
<form action="" method="post">
<br/><label for="poll-ip-textbox">Poll IP:</label>
<input id="poll-ip-textbox" name="poll-ip-textbox" type="text" value="0.0.0.0" disabled />
<br/><label for="poll-port-textbox">Poll Port:</label>
<input id="poll-port-textbox" name="poll-port-textbox" type="text" value="0" disabled />
Via node:<input id="via-node-chkbox" name="via-node-chkbox" type="checkbox" value="Through node" />
Via proxy:<input id="via-node-chkbox" name="via-node-chkbox" type="checkbox" value="Through node" />
<br/><input id="start-poll-button" type="button" value="Start poll"/>
<br/><input id="stop-poll-button" type="button" value="Stop poll"/>
</form>
<div id="pods">Pods&colon;<br/></div>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js" integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="./index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
